2) Tool-to-Flow Mapping (What exactly runs)
Tool	Purpose	Internal path in current code
vajra_ask	Natural-language query/lookup/docs	LangGraph agent via langgraph_app.ainvoke(...)
vajra_resolve_service	Remediate vulnerabilities for one service	resolve_service(...) from vajra_routes.py
vajra_upgrade_library	Upgrade one specific dependency + PR	GithubService.specific_lib_upgrade(...)
vajra_scan_dependencies	Trigger dependency scan workflow	_safe_github_workflow_dispatch(...)
3) Example Runtime Flows
