4) Compliance Alignment (Current Architecture Intent)
This flow is compliant with enterprise architecture intent when routed through Agentic Gateway:

centralized auth and coarse-grained authorization
guardrails and rate limits at gateway layer
logs/traces for auditability
controlled tool invocation path (no direct ad-hoc backend calls)
