8) MCP Payload and Response Contracts (Exact)
This section shows the exact request/response shapes Voice should expect when calling Vajra via MCP.

8.1 Initialize handshake
Request:

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "method": "initialize",
  "params": {}
}
Response:

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "result": {
    "protocolVersion": "2025-03-26",
    "capabilities": {
      "tools": {
        "listChanged": false
      }
    },
    "serverInfo": {
      "name": "vajra-mcp-server",
      "version": "1.0.0"
    }
  }
}
8.2 Tool discovery (tools/list)
Request:

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 2,
  "method": "tools/list",
  "params": {}
}
Response shape:

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 2,
  "result": {
    "tools": [
      {
        "name": "vajra_ask",
        "description": "...",
        "inputSchema": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "prompt": { "type": "string" },
            "session_id": { "type": "string" }
          },
          "required": ["prompt"]
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
8.3 Tool invocation (tools/call)
Request template:

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 3,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "<tool_name>",
    "arguments": {
      "...": "..."
    }
  }
}
Response template (success):

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 3,
  "result": {
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "{\"success\":true,\"response\":\"...\"}"
      }
    ],
    "isError": false
  }
}
Response template (tool-level failure):

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 3,
  "result": {
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "{\"success\":false,\"error\":\"...\"}"
      }
    ],
    "isError": true
  }
}
Response template (protocol-level failure):

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 3,
  "error": {
    "code": -32601,
    "message": "Tool not found: <name>. Available: ..."
  }
}
